{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4e/78/195636_crt_I2IOu.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4e/78/195636_crt_I2IOu.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4e/78/195636_crt_I2IOu.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/4e/78/195636_crt_I2IOu.jpg"},"name":"ジョシュア・グラント","summary":"名門グラント一族の娘とロレート公国公子の子息。父母を幼いときになくし、母方の伯父の家で育つ。13歳で聖アルフォンソ学院に入学。正義感・責任感があり 、周囲からの信頼も厚い。しかし時折、人を寄せ付けない雰囲気を見せることがある。生徒代表。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg"},"name":"置鮎龍太郎","short_summary":"日本の男性声優、ナレーターである。青二プロダクション所属。血液型はO型。\r\n\r\n妻は声優の前田愛。置鮎は再婚となる。前妻は声優の永澤菜教。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":3976,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":195636},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/53/ab/195637_crt_S78Rz.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/53/ab/195637_crt_S78Rz.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/53/ab/195637_crt_S78Rz.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/53/ab/195637_crt_S78Rz.jpg"},"name":"ユウタ","summary":"視聴者の弟。外国に留学したいと思っていた矢先、親の知り合いである外国人の富豪に聖アルフォンソ学院を薦められ、単身留学を決意。16歳で入学。学院の特殊事情にあまり動じず、生来の性格の良さで誰とでも仲良くなる。ジョシュアたち5人とは同じ寮で暮らす。非常に姉想いの弟。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a2/79/4416_prsn_nsNHF.jpg?r=1584943089","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a2/79/4416_prsn_nsNHF.jpg?r=1584943089","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a2/79/4416_prsn_nsNHF.jpg?r=1584943089","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a2/79/4416_prsn_nsNHF.jpg?r=1584943089"},"name":"菅沼久義","short_summary":"日本男性声优，擅长演出少年、青年的声线。代表作是天使的尾巴的睦悟郎，真·三国无双系列的孙权、姜维。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":4416,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":195637},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/30/4f/195638_crt_XCrY4.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/30/4f/195638_crt_XCrY4.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/30/4f/195638_crt_XCrY4.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/30/4f/195638_crt_XCrY4.jpg"},"name":"アルフレッド・ヴィスコンティ","summary":"芸能一家に生まれるサラブレッドの俳優。祖父は名監督。父はTVプロデューサー。5歳のころからデビューし、人気子役に。16歳で聖アルフォンソ学院に入学。プレイボーイで誰にでも愛想が良い。自信家。ただし、演技についてだけは真摯で完ぺき主義者。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673"},"name":"森田成一","short_summary":"日本の声優、俳優、ナレーターである。血液型はA型。\r\n特技  剣道、空手\r\n趣味  写真撮影、クラシックカメラ収集、各種モノ作り\r\n\r\n芸歴\r\n2003年　青二プロダクション\r\n2021年　フリー\r\n2025年　ステイラック","career":["seiyu","actor"],"id":4716,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":195638},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/07/ee/195639_crt_80Si8.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/07/ee/195639_crt_80Si8.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/07/ee/195639_crt_80Si8.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/07/ee/195639_crt_80Si8.jpg"},"name":"アンリ=ユーグ=ド=サン・ジェルマン","summary":"錬金術師とも山師ともいわれる伝説的貴族、サン・ジェルマン伯爵の直系の子孫。13歳で聖アルフォンソ学院に入学。美貌めあてで近づく人に対してはそれなりの対応。毒舌家。基本的に人を信用しない。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/62/de/3850_prsn_6dp69.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/62/de/3850_prsn_6dp69.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/62/de/3850_prsn_6dp69.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/62/de/3850_prsn_6dp69.jpg"},"name":"野島健児","short_summary":"日本の男性声優、歌手、ナレーターである。青二プロダクション所属。\r\n東京都杉並区出身。身長163cm、血液型はA型。父の野島昭生、兄の野島裕史は共に声優。弟は作家の野島智司。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":3850,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":195639},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/01/17/195640_crt_1DZ2S.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/01/17/195640_crt_1DZ2S.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/01/17/195640_crt_1DZ2S.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/01/17/195640_crt_1DZ2S.jpg"},"name":"シルヴァン・クラーク","summary":"名門軍人の家系。父の仕事の関係で様々な都市を転々とする日々。母親は画家。2年前、17歳で聖アルフォンソ学院に入学。最初は反発したが、持ち前の転校生体質ですぐに適応し、学院生活を謳歌中。数カ国語を話す。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/da/3c/9847_prsn_jJeNl.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/da/3c/9847_prsn_jJeNl.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/da/3c/9847_prsn_jJeNl.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/da/3c/9847_prsn_jJeNl.jpg"},"name":"三宅淳一","short_summary":"三宅 淳一（みやけ じゅんいち、1980年1月13日 - ）は日本の男性声優。青二プロダクション所属。東京都生まれの神奈川県横浜市育ち。血液型はO型。\r\nBoy's Beatのメンバー（他のメンバーに岡本寛志、根本幸多、鈴木賢、河本啓佑）。","career":["seiyu"],"id":9847,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":195640},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6e/95/195641_crt_N4LJF.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6e/95/195641_crt_N4LJF.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6e/95/195641_crt_N4LJF.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6e/95/195641_crt_N4LJF.jpg"},"name":"小林春也","summary":"祖父は名家の当主、母は芸妓。踊りの名手である母のお稽古事についていったため、幼い頃から日舞や茶道に親しむ。16歳で聖アルフォンソ学院に入学。人当たりは柔らく、飄々とした性格。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/c6/94/5261_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c6/94/5261_seiyu_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c6/94/5261_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/c6/94/5261_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},"name":"岡本寛志","short_summary":"日本の男性声優。青二プロダクション所属。奈良県出身。","career":["seiyu"],"id":5261,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":195641},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/46/4f/195642_crt_Jx636.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/46/4f/195642_crt_Jx636.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/46/4f/195642_crt_Jx636.jpg","medi